    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy! This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014it honestly looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom. I\u2019ve babied this thing from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stayed spotless. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
