    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a mechanically flawless E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system. This example boasts a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, ensuring direct engagement and precise gear synchronization. The chassis is in exemplary state, with no signs of the common RACP (Rear Axle Carrier Panel) stress fractures. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing factory-spec bushings and dampers that provide the signature M-division feedback. Every fluid service is up to date, including the critical 1,200-mile break-in and subsequent Valve Clearance Inspections. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
